---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Disciples d'Escoffier Provence Méditerranée">
  <section class="relative pt-28 pb-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-5 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="lg:text-5xl text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 text-center">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <hr class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full" />
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto mt-16">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            About this policy
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            The Disciples d'Escoffier Provence Méditerranée association is
            committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This policy
            explains how we collect, use and protect your personal data when you
            use our website and our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          1. Data Controller
        </h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <p>
            <strong>Data Controller:</strong> Association Disciples d'Escoffier Provence
            Méditerranée
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Address:</strong> CFA COROT - PARC MASSILLIA 33 BOULEVARD DU
            CAPITAINE GEZE 13014 MARSEILLE
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> contact@disciplesescoffier-provence-mediterranee.org
          </p>
          <p><strong>Representative:</strong> Alain Laporte</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          2. Data Collected
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
            2.1 Data collected via the contact form
          </h3>
          <p>
            When you use our contact form to join us, we collect the following
            information:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 marker:text-black">
            <li>
              <strong>Identification information:</strong> first name, last name
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Contact details:</strong> email address, phone number (optional)
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Professional information:</strong> profession
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Geographic information:</strong> city, postal code
            </li>
            <li><strong>Message:</strong> your motivation message</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6">
            2.2 Navigation data
          </h3>
          <p>
            We automatically collect certain technical information when you
            visit our site:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 marker:text-black">
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Pages visited and visit duration</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>Approximate location data (country, region)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          3. Processing Purposes
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>We use your personal data for the following purposes:</p>

          <div class="bg-secondary/50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-black">
              3.1 Membership application management
            </h4>
            <p>
              Processing and follow-up of your request to join our association.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Legal basis:</strong> Consent and legitimate interest
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-secondary/50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-black">3.2 Communication</h4>
            <p>
              Respond to your questions and inform you about our activities.
            </p>
            <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Consent</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-secondary/50 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-black">3.3 Website improvement</h4>
            <p>Analyze site usage to improve user experience.</p>
            <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Legitimate interest</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          4. Retention Period
        </h2>
        <div class="text-black space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-primary/20 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 marker:text-black">
              <li>
                <strong>Contact form data:</strong> 3 years maximum from the last
                interaction
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Navigation data:</strong> 13 months maximum
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Active members:</strong> During membership period + 5 years
                after end of membership
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Unsuccessful applications:</strong> 2 years maximum
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p>
            Upon expiration of these periods, your data is securely deleted or
            anonymized.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          5. Data Recipients
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>Your personal data is accessible to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 marker:text-black">
            <li>
              <strong>Internally:</strong> To association board members responsible
              for recruitment and communication
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Technical service providers:</strong> Our web host and our
              email service (Brevo) within the strict framework of their services
            </li>
            <li><strong>Authorities:</strong> Only if required by law</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We do not sell, rent or share your data for commercial purposes with
            third parties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          6. Your Rights
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>In accordance with GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Right of access</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Obtain a copy of your personal data</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                Right of rectification
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Correct inaccurate or incomplete data</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Right to erasure</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Request deletion of your data</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                Right to restriction
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Limit the processing of your data</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
                Right to portability
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Retrieve your data in a readable format</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Right to object</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Object to the processing of your data</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-container p-4 rounded-lg mt-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">
              How to exercise your rights?
            </h4>
            <p>
              To exercise these rights, contact us at:
              <a
                href="mailto:contact@disciplesescoffier-provence-mediterranee.org"
                class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline"
              >
                contact@disciplesescoffier-provence-mediterranee.org
              </a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2">
              We will respond within a maximum of 30 days. A piece of
              identification may be requested to verify your identity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          7. Data Security
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to
            protect your data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 marker:text-black">
            <li>
              <strong>Encryption:</strong> Secure transmission via HTTPS
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Restricted access:</strong> Only authorized persons can access
              your data
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Backup:</strong> Regular and secure data backup
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Training:</strong> Awareness of our teams on data protection
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Updates:</strong> Regular maintenance of our security systems
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          8. Cookies and Similar Technologies
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">8.1 Cookies used</h3>
          <p>
            Our site uses only technical cookies necessary for proper
            functioning:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 marker:text-black">
            <li>
              <strong>Session cookies:</strong> Maintaining your browsing session
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Preference cookies:</strong> Saving your preferences (e.g.:
              disabling custom cursor)
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Security cookies:</strong> Protection against multiple form
              submissions
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-4">
            8.2 Cookie management
          </h3>
          <p>
            You can configure your browser to refuse cookies. However, this may
            affect the proper functioning of the site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          9. Data Transfers
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>
            Your data is mainly processed within the European Union. In cases
            where data would be transferred outside the EU (for example, via our
            emailing service Brevo), we ensure that appropriate safeguards are
            in place (standard contractual clauses, adequacy decision).
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          10. Right to Complaint
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>
            If you believe that the processing of your personal data constitutes
            a violation of GDPR, you have the right to lodge a complaint with
            the CNIL:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <p>
              <strong
                >CNIL - National Commission for Information Technology and Civil
                Liberties</strong
              >
            </p>
            <p>3 Place de Fontenoy - TSA 80715 - 75334 PARIS CEDEX 07</p>
            <p>Phone: 01 53 73 22 22</p>
            <p>
              Website: <a
                href="https://www.cnil.fr"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline"
                >www.cnil.fr</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          11. Policy Modifications
        </h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time. Any
            modification will be published on this page with an update date. We
            encourage you to consult this page regularly.
          </p>
          <p>
            In case of substantial modification, we will inform you by email if
            we have your address.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-container p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">
            Contact and questions
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            For any questions regarding this privacy policy or the processing of
            your personal data, please do not hesitate to contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p>
              <strong>Email:</strong>
              <a
                href="mailto:contact@disciplesescoffier-provence-mediterranee.org"
                class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline"
              >
                contact@disciplesescoffier-provence-mediterranee.org
              </a>
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>Mail:</strong> CFA COROT - PARC MASSILLIA 33 BOULEVARD DU CAPITAINE
              GEZE 13014 MARSEILLE
            </p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-4">
            <strong>Last updated:</strong>
            {new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US")}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
